Class RangeSliderUI

  • Object
    • ComponentUI
      • SliderUI

          • RangeSliderUI

  • public class RangeSliderUI
extends BasicSliderUI
    UI delegate for the RangeSlider component. RangeSliderUI paints two thumbs, one for the lower value and one for the upper value.
    Author:
    Ernie Yu, LimeWire LLC
